8月3日，一股[[东风波|东风波]]在[[维尔京群岛|维尔京群岛]]北面发展成热带气旋<ref name="documentation">{{cite report | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150930195553/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/metadata_dec12.html | archivedate = 2015-09-30 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/metadata_dec12.html | title = Documentation of Atlantic Tropical Cyclones Changes in HURDAT | author = Christopher W. Landsea | date = 2012-12 | work = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2017-01-12 | location = Miami, Florida | display-authors = etal }}</ref>。系统存在的大部分时间都是沿[[大安的列斯群岛|大安的列斯群岛]]海岸平行移动，于8月6日在[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]上空增强成一级飓风。风暴继续强化，成为二级飓风后又于8月7日达到[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]每小时165公里的最高强度。不久，气旋经小幅减弱于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]8月8日早上7点从[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]][[匹尔斯堡_(佛罗里达州)|匹尔斯堡]]附近[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]。接下来一天里风暴在穿越佛罗里达州期间逐渐减弱，其间短暂进入[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]上空，但很快又转向北上。8月10日，气旋以热带风暴强度登陆佛罗里达州西北狭长地带，在进入陆地上空后继续减弱，于当天消退成热带低气压并逐渐转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]。系统的温带残留进入[[大西洋|大西洋]]，最终于8月14日逐渐消散。<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | accessdate = 2016-11-01 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2016-07-06 | archivedate = 2016-10-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161004150702/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] | deadurl = no }}</ref>

气旋存在早期，尚在大安的列斯群岛北侧海域时就对巴哈马的航运构成影响，[[古巴|古巴]]近海波涛汹涌<ref name="Miss">{{cite news | title = Storm Curves Away; Florida to Miss Blow | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=4t8cAAAAIBAJ&sjid=H2QEAAAAIBAJ&pg=5175,6300113&dq=hurricane&hl=en | accessdate = 2017-01-12 | newspaper = Sarasota Herald-Tribune | date = 1928-08-06 | location = Miami, Florida | page = 1 | archive-date = 2020-12-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201226115150/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=4t8cAAAAIBAJ&sjid=H2QEAAAAIBAJ&pg=5175%2C6300113&dq=hurricane&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="CubaSea">{{cite news | title = Heavy Sea on Cuban Coast | location = Havana, Cuba | page = 12 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=Rt9PAAAAIBAJ&sjid=l1QDAAAAIBAJ&pg=4902,6460002&dq=hurricane&hl=en | accessdate = 2017-01-12 | newspaper = The Evening Independent | date = 1928-08-08 | agency = Associated Press | archive-date = 2020-12-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201226115101/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=Rt9PAAAAIBAJ&sjid=l1QDAAAAIBAJ&pg=4902%2C6460002&dq=hurricane&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。风暴登陆匹尔斯堡期间对多地构成重大破坏，并以沿海地区灾情严重，许多民宅失去屋顶<ref name="Isolation">{{cite news | title = Tampa Isolated by Florida Storm | accessdate = 2017-01-12 | newspaper = Painesville Telegraph | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=AbZZAAAAIBAJ&sjid=DUoNAAAAIBAJ&pg=1588,3498529&dq=hurricane&hl=en | agency = Associated Press | location = Jacksonville, Florida | page = 1 | date = 1928-08-09 | archive-date = 2020-12-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201226115107/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=AbZZAAAAIBAJ&sjid=DUoNAAAAIBAJ&pg=1588%2C3498529&dq=hurricane&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[中佛罗里达|中佛罗里达]]的柑橘作物受到狂风暴雨破坏<ref name="documentation" />，包括[[奥基乔比湖|奥基乔比湖]]在内多个湖泊的湖水泛滥，将沿岸地区淹没<ref name="Sweep">{{cite news | title = Hurricane Sweeps to Gulf | agency = Associated Press | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=tFlGAAAAIBAJ&sjid=vycNAAAAIBAJ&pg=4140,4632722&dq=hurricane&hl=en | accessdate = 2017-01-17 | newspaper = Rochester Evening Journal and the Post Express | date = 1928-08-09 | location = Jacksonville, Florida | page = 2 | archive-date = 2020-12-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201226115112/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=tFlGAAAAIBAJ&sjid=vycNAAAAIBAJ&pg=4140%2C4632722&dq=hurricane&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="gripGale">{{cite news | title = Florida in Grip of Gale | page = 9 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=5fE0AAAAIBAJ&sjid=umcFAAAAIBAJ&pg=855,2811601&dq=hurricane&hl=en | accessdate = 2017-01-12 | newspaper = Lewiston Evening Journal | date = 1928-08-08 | agency = Associated Press | location = Melbourne, Florida | archive-date = 2020-12-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201226115117/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=5fE0AAAAIBAJ&sjid=umcFAAAAIBAJ&pg=855%2C2811601&dq=hurricane&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。内陆地区的基础设施受损程度比沿海要轻，但停电依然导致大范围通讯中断<ref name="RoofsOff">{{cite news | title = Roofs Off at Kissimmee | agency = Associated Press | location = Tampa, Florida | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=R99PAAAAIBAJ&sjid=l1QDAAAAIBAJ&pg=5588,6562911&dq=hurricane&hl=en | accessdate = 2017-01-12 | newspaper = The Evening Independent | date = 1928-08-09 | page = 1 | archive-date = 2020-12-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201226115126/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=R99PAAAAIBAJ&sjid=l1QDAAAAIBAJ&pg=5588%2C6562911&dq=hurricane&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。飓风第二次登陆期间的风害相对较小，但瓢泼大雨和[[地形抬升|地形抬升]]因素共同影响，引发大面积洪灾，影响范围向北一直延伸到[[中大西洋地区|中大西洋地区]]<ref name="rainfall">{{cite web | title = Rainfall Associated With Hurricanes (And Other Tropical Disturbances) | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/1956NHRPreportNo3.pdf | publisher = United States Weather Bureau's National Hurricane Research Project | accessdate = 2017-01-12 | author1 = R. W. Schoner | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161229173023/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/1956NHRPreportNo3.pdf | author2 = S. Molansky | page = 84 | archivedate = 2016-12-29 | deadurl = no | format = PDF }}</ref>。整场飓风一共导致两人死亡和23.5万美元的经济损失，其中大部分发生在佛罗里达州<ref name="documentation" />。
