8月7日，一股东风波在[[多巴哥|多巴哥]]附近发展成热带低气压<ref name="documentation" />。系统从[[卡里亚库和小马提尼克|卡里亚库和小马提尼克]]南侧近海经过[[向风群岛|向风群岛]]，于8月8日清晨进入加勒比海后增强成热带风暴。8月9日，气旋在[[多米尼加|多米尼加共和国]]南面达到一级飓风标准，再于次日达到风力时速150公里的最高强度。袭击[[海地|海地]]蒂伯龙半岛（{{lang|en|Tiburon Peninsula}}）后，风暴开始减弱，强度在8月12日回落至热带风暴标准。8月13日中午，气旋已从古巴[[西恩富戈斯|西恩富戈斯]]附近登陆。进入[[佛罗里达海峡|佛罗里达海峡]]后，风暴重新增强，于8月13日清晨以强烈热带风暴强度吹袭[[门罗县_(佛罗里达州)|门罗县]][[大松礁岛_(佛罗里达州)|大松礁岛]]（{{lang|en|Big Pine Key}}）。气旋向西北偏北移动并缓慢减弱，然后又从[[富兰克林县_(佛罗里达州)|富兰克林县]][[圣乔治岛_(佛罗里达州)|圣乔治岛]]（{{lang|en|St. George Island}}）附近登陆。风暴进入陆地上空后缓慢消退，于8月15日弱化成热带低气压，最终于8月17日在[[西弗吉尼亚州|西弗吉尼亚州]]上空逐渐消散。<ref name="HURDAT" />

风暴将海地几乎所有的牲畜和大量农作物卷走，咖啡、可可和制糖作物受灾特别严重<ref name="to">{{cite news | url = http://trove.nla.gov.au/newspaper/article/164861269?searchTerm=haiti%20hurricane&searchLimits=sortby=dateAsc | title = Haiti Hurricane | date = 1928-09-08 | newspaper = The Observer | pages = 56 | accessdate = 2017-01-12 | location = New York | archive-date = 2020-11-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201129191607/https://trove.nla.gov.au/newspaper/article/164861269?searchTerm=haiti%20hurricane&searchLimits=sortby=dateAsc | dead-url = no }}</ref>。多个村庄毁于一旦，致使约一万人无家可归，损失总额达到100万美元，至少有200人遇难<ref name="ct">{{cite news | title = Haiti Hurricane Leaves Death, Chaos In Wake | date = 1928-08-19 | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = [[芝加哥论坛报|Chicago Tribune]] | page = 3 | accessdate = 2017-01-12 | location = Port-au-Prince, Haiti | url = http://archives.chicagotribune.com/1928/08/19/page/3/article/reed-declares-drys-scheme-to-ruin-democrats | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160307202250/http://archives.chicagotribune.com/1928/08/19/page/3/article/reed-declares-drys-scheme-to-ruin-democrats/ | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-07 }}</ref>。古巴所受影响基本局限于香蕉树倒塌<ref name="documentation" />。佛罗里达州沿海地区受到轻度破坏，[[博卡格兰德_(佛罗里达州)|博卡格兰德]]（{{lang|en|Boca Grande}}）的一个火车站被毁，[[萨拉索塔_(佛罗里达州)|萨拉索培]]部分标志牌、树木和电线杆倒塌，[[圣彼德斯堡_(佛罗里达州)|圣彼德斯堡]]部分街道因洪水或瓦砾影响暂时封闭<ref>{{cite news | newspaper = St. Petersburg Times | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=hylPAAAAIBAJ&sjid=xk0DAAAAIBAJ&pg=6818%2C2322269 | title = Pass-a-Grille Warned Against High Tides Today Following Tropical Gale Which Swept Entire West Coast but Caused Little Damage | date = 1928-08-14 | pages = 1–2 | accessdate = 2017-01-12 | archive-date = 2020-12-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201226115141/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=hylPAAAAIBAJ&sjid=xk0DAAAAIBAJ&pg=6818%2C2322269 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[锡达礁_(佛罗里达州)|锡达礁]]至佛罗里达州西北狭长地带之间有许多船只倾覆，洪水还对道路和树木构成冲刷<ref>{{cite news | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=iSlPAAAAIBAJ&sjid=xk0DAAAAIBAJ&pg=5643%2C2470198 | title = Boats Wrecked, Hodges Reports | date = 1928-08-16 | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = St. Petersburg Times | page = 2 | accessdate = 2017-01-12 | location = Tallahassee, Florida | archive-date = 2020-12-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201226122713/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=iSlPAAAAIBAJ&sjid=xk0DAAAAIBAJ&pg=5643%2C2470198 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。风暴致使此前由第一号飓风引发的洪灾复发，各地以[[南卡罗莱纳州|南卡罗莱纳州]][[格林维尔县_(南卡罗莱纳州)|格林维尔县]]的凯撒黑德（{{lang|en|Caesars Head}}）雨量最高，达340毫米<ref>{{cite book | page = SA 2–13 | title = Storm Total Rainfall In The United States | author = United States Corp of Engineers | publisher = War Department | date = 1945}}</ref>。[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]]的洪灾最为严重，许多房屋被毁。该州有六人死亡，其中四人死于洪灾，经济损失总额超过100万美元<ref name="hdn">{{cite news | newspaper = Huntingdon Daily News | date = 1928-08-17 | title = Ten Die in Tropical Storm that Hits Southern States}}</ref>。整场飓风一共造成至少210人死亡，经济损失约为200万美元<ref name="ct" /><ref name="hdn" />。
{{clear}}

